                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/behat/edit/behat3/knpu/scenario-outline.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Add a second scenario to search: searching for a product that is <em>not</em> found.
I'm lazy, so I'll copy the first scenario.</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="cdee53aaba">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
