<p>It <em>is</em> ok not to have any <code>Given</code>'s in the scenario and start directly with
<code>When</code>. I'll change the search term to "XBox" - none of those in the dino store.
This is really going to bum out any dino's that are looking to play Ghost Recon.</p>
<p>When there are no matches - the site says "No Products Found". Cool, let's plug
