</p>
<p>Now, we have two variable parts. To fill those in, add an <code>Examples</code> section at the end
with a little table that has <code>term</code> and <code>result</code> columns. For the first row, use <code>Samsung</code>
for the <code>term</code> and <code>Samsung Galaxy</code> for the <code>result</code>. The second row should be <code>XBox</code>
and the <code>No products found</code> message:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="7ed8e7bb11">
    <div class="meta">
